Patrik Svensson | GitHub Stars
Patrik is a Microsoft MVP and open-source contributor who has been a professional programmer for 16 years. He's probably best known as the creator of the Cake build system and Spectre.Console, a library that makes it easy to build beautiful console applications in .NET. Apart from C#, he likes to contribute to open-source, DevOps, and Rust (the programming language).
